                   StringParseException,
                   MandatoryMapValueNotFoundException,
                   MandatorySimpleArgumentNotFoundException
Tests whether the parser will put all trailing arguments in an array. The simple argument MyOptionsEndingInArray.a3() is an array. So all simple arguments after the second should go to MyOptionsEndingInArray.a3(). On the other hand, if there are only two arguments, the value of MyOptionsEndingInArray.a3() should be an empty array.
